{"tid":1965520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃店《潮食閣》成功申請成為勵敬懲教所<私人膳食供應商>！","createTime":"2020-04-09T13:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T07:17:48.000Z","uid":244704,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"050d34eb9871df2a9614479933484006ce3eff3b","tid":1965520,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:44:46.000Z","msg":"特別通告，我們終於申請成功，<br />\n成為勵敬懲教所&lt;私人膳食供應商&gt;！<br />\n<br />\n我們將於2020年4月20日開始為還押人士提供私人膳食。就算裡面只有一位手足，我們也務必提供溫暖、飽肚的膳食給她們。我們承諾必定不會讓她們肚餓😭。<br />\n<br />\n我們特別想講，多謝邵家臻議員，梁錦威團隊及懲教署更生事務組，一直密切關注及改善在囚人士的情況，部份手足更被還押超過100天的😭。希望大家可以繼續關注入面手足的情況🙏，給予多一些支持，告訴他們「我們從來沒有忘記過仼何一位」。<br />\n<br />\n最後我們想講，我們也正耐心等候荔枝角收押所及壁屋懲教所的消息，我們也希望盡快成為他們的供應商。&lt;正義或許會遲到，但絕不會缺席&gt;，希望大家也要堅持下去💪。<br />\n<br />\n#勿忘手足 #香港人加油<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hp3EJhD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhp3EJhD.jpg&h=579270d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yummycornerhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyummycornerhk%2F&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVaCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=232eeb0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yummycornerhk/</a>"},{"pid":"be27be0d298b6173f7c683f97b684de16d385880","tid":1965520,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:50:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a4a5494770c60871d82215509fbc0e9d21e15b","tid":1965520,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:53:49.000Z","msg":"e間唔係炸野小食架咩，有做正餐架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ff4666137d7e2bd6b945237766453ac71b9a82","tid":1965520,"uid":168903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"